============================================================
Functional calculus, not taxonomy.

LAYER 1 — META-LANGUAGE
    Rules for talking about language.

LAYER 2 — STRUCTURAL OPERATORS 
    Rules for analyzing language.

LAYER 3 — LANGUAGE OBJECTS
    Actual languages as geometric objects.

